{"tid":1878164,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我有方法完全逃避情人節。","createTime":"2020-02-13T12:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T16:34:58.000Z","uid":107092,"like":226,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1024238cdd33c070049df615013b549a32f22835","tid":1878164,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:19:55.000Z","msg":"我有方法完全逃避情人節，<br />\n就係而家即刻飛去美屬薩摩亞，<br />\n佢係位於UTC-11嘅時區，<br />\n全世界最後慶祝新年嘅地方。<br />\n當去到當地時間2月13日嘅夜晚11點嘅一刻，<br />\n我就坐船過去，冇錯，<br />\n係坐船過去旁邊嘅薩摩亞獨立國。<br />\n<br />\n由於嗰處係行緊夏令時間UTC+14，<br />\n我將會由UTC-11 2月13日23:00，<br />\n踏入UTC+14 2月15日 02:00。<br />\n換言之，我穿越咗時空，<br />\n從來冇喺2020年2月14日出現過。"},{"pid":"5127af7025c832d89526d80bc7afdfa92ac63c80","tid":1878164,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84f1cb7569b186901cc355868ff2528e83c45ef","tid":1878164,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646d737a7195566369e4c39b33124fae8d2ffa8e","tid":1878164,"uid":284127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dee5139412472241fbb7af3c3d969d93e0f1f74","tid":1878164,"uid":283908,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"王家衛上身?"},{"pid":"ae31e234741af421abc0718ee32bf1f144e1c2cd","tid":1878164,"uid":179975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4dd7d32890302e695a3230c8eaa7be9c65b8db","tid":1878164,"uid":251581,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:26:49.000Z","msg":"我鍾意你既思路"},{"pid":"ff3c5c33b2e0c053767642194fe3f19b23b4cb7f","tid":1